thread.title: ASUS ZenFone 3 series, ZenFone 2 Laser and ZenFone Max get VoLTE update in India
thread.title_full: ASUS ZenFone 3 series, ZenFone 2 Laser and ZenFone Max get VoLTE update in India

title: ASUS ZenFone 3 series, ZenFone 2 Laser and ZenFone Max get VoLTE update in India
text:
ASUS ZenFone 3 series, ZenFone 2 Laser and ZenFone Max get VoLTE... ASUS ZenFone 3 series, ZenFone 2 Laser and ZenFone Max get VoLTE update in India By February 17, 2017 “The ASUS ZenFone 3 Ultra and ZenFone Selfie will get the VoLTE update soon” 
ASUS has started rolling out VoLTE updates to its ZenFone 3 range in India. In addition, the brand has also released VoLTE support for the ZenFone Max , ZenFone 2 Laser and ZenFone Go 5.0 LTE . 
The ZenFone series phones getting the update include the ZenFone 3 Deluxe , ZenFone 3 Laser , ZenFone 3 Max and ZenFone 3S Max . It’s worth mentioning the ZenFone 3 that comes in 5.2-inch and 5.5-inch sizes already had VoLTE support earlier. The brand will soon be releasing VoLTE support for the ZenFone 3 Ultra and ZenFone Selfie in the coming weeks. Facebook Comments
